{"snp3.5:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 3.5 ","snp3.5:0.2":"Maghasutta ","snp3.5:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","snp3.5:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava rajagahe viharati gijjhakute pabbate. ","snp3.5:1.3":"Atha kho magho manavo yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavata saddhim sammodi. ","snp3.5:1.4":"Sammodaniyam katham saraniyam vitisaretva ekamantam nisidi. ","snp3.5:1.5":"Ekamantam nisinno kho magho manavo bhagavantam etadavoca: ","snp3.5:2.1":"“Ahanhi, bho gotama, dayako danapati vadannu yacayogo; ","snp3.5:2.2":"dhammena bhoge pariyesami; ","snp3.5:2.3":"dhammena bhoge pariyesitva dhammaladdhehi bhogehi dhammadhigatehi ekassapi dadami dvinnampi tinnampi catunnampi pancannampi channampi sattannampi atthannampi navannampi dasannampi dadami, visayapi timsayapi cattalisayapi pannasayapi dadami, satassapi dadami, bhiyyopi dadami. ","snp3.5:2.4":"Kaccaham, bho gotama, evam dadanto evam yajanto bahum punnam pasavami”ti? ","snp3.5:3.1":"“Taggha tvam, manava, evam dadanto evam yajanto bahum punnam pasavasi. ","snp3.5:3.2":"Yo kho, manava, dayako danapati vadannu yacayogo; ","snp3.5:3.3":"dhammena bhoge pariyesati; ","snp3.5:3.4":"dhammena bhoge pariyesitva dhammaladdhehi bhogehi dhammadhigatehi ekassapi dadati …pe… satassapi dadati, bhiyyopi dadati, bahum so punnam pasavati”ti. ","snp3.5:3.5":"Atha kho magho manavo bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi—","snp3.5:4.1":"“Pucchamaham gotamam vadannum, ","snp3.5:4.2":"(iti magho manavo) ","snp3.5:4.3":"Kasayavasim agaham carantam; ","snp3.5:4.4":"Yo yacayogo danapati gahattho, ","snp3.5:4.5":"Punnatthiko yajati punnapekkho; ","snp3.5:4.6":"Dadam paresam idha annapanam, ","snp3.5:4.7":"Katham hutam yajamanassa sujjhe”. ","snp3.5:5.1":"“Yo yacayogo danapati gahattho, ","snp3.5:5.2":"(maghati bhagava) ","snp3.5:5.3":"Punnatthiko yajati punnapekkho; ","snp3.5:5.4":"Dadam paresam idha annapanam, ","snp3.5:5.5":"Aradhaye dakkhineyyebhi tadi”. ","snp3.5:6.1":"“Yo yacayogo danapati gahattho, ","snp3.5:6.2":"(iti magho manavo) ","snp3.5:6.3":"Punnatthiko yajati punnapekkho; ","snp3.5:6.4":"Dadam paresam idha annapanam, ","snp3.5:6.5":"Akkhahi me bhagava dakkhineyye”. ","snp3.5:7.1":"“Ye ve asatta vicaranti loke, ","snp3.5:7.2":"Akincana kevalino yatatta; ","snp3.5:7.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:7.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:8.1":"Ye sabbasamyojanabandhanacchida, ","snp3.5:8.2":"Danta vimutta anigha nirasa; ","snp3.5:8.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:8.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:9.1":"Ye sabbasamyojanavippamutta, ","snp3.5:9.2":"Danta vimutta anigha nirasa; ","snp3.5:9.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:9.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:10.1":"Raganca dosanca pahaya moham, ","snp3.5:10.2":"Khinasava vusitabrahmacariya; ","snp3.5:10.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:10.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:11.1":"Yesu na maya vasati na mano, ","snp3.5:11.2":"Khinasava vusitabrahmacariya; ","snp3.5:11.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:11.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:12.1":"Ye vitalobha amama nirasa, ","snp3.5:12.2":"Khinasava vusitabrahmacariya; ","snp3.5:12.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:12.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:13.1":"Ye ve na tanhasu upatipanna, ","snp3.5:13.2":"Vitareyya ogham amama caranti; ","snp3.5:13.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:13.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:14.1":"Yesam tanha natthi kuhinci loke, ","snp3.5:14.2":"Bhavabhavaya idha va huram va; ","snp3.5:14.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:14.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:15.1":"Ye kame hitva agaha caranti, ","snp3.5:15.2":"Susannatatta tasaramva ujjum; ","snp3.5:15.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:15.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:16.1":"Ye vitaraga susamahitindriya, ","snp3.5:16.2":"Candova rahuggahana pamutta; ","snp3.5:16.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:16.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:17.1":"Samitavino vitaraga akopa, ","snp3.5:17.2":"Yesam gati natthidha vippahaya; ","snp3.5:17.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:17.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:18.1":"Jahitva jatimaranam asesam, ","snp3.5:18.2":"Kathankathim sabbamupativatta; ","snp3.5:18.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:18.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:19.1":"Ye attadipa vicaranti loke, ","snp3.5:19.2":"Akincana sabbadhi vippamutta; ","snp3.5:19.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:19.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:20.1":"Ye hettha jananti yatha tatha idam, ","snp3.5:20.2":"Ayamantima natthi punabbhavoti; ","snp3.5:20.3":"Kalena tesu habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:20.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha. ","snp3.5:21.1":"Yo vedagu jhanarato satima, ","snp3.5:21.2":"Sambodhipatto saranam bahunam; ","snp3.5:21.3":"Kalena tamhi habyam pavecche, ","snp3.5:21.4":"Yo brahmano punnapekkho yajetha”. ","snp3.5:22.1":"“Addha amogha mama pucchana ahu, ","snp3.5:22.2":"(iti magho manavo) ","snp3.5:22.3":"Akkhasi me bhagava dakkhineyye; ","snp3.5:22.4":"Tvanhettha janasi yatha tatha idam, ","snp3.5:22.5":"Tatha hi te vidito esa dhammo. ","snp3.5:23.1":"Yo yacayogo danapati gahattho, ","snp3.5:23.2":"Punnatthiko yajati punnapekkho; ","snp3.5:23.3":"Dadam paresam idha annapanam, ","snp3.5:23.4":"Akkhahi me bhagava yannasampadam”. ","snp3.5:24.1":"“Yajassu yajamano, ","snp3.5:24.2":"(maghati bhagava) ","snp3.5:24.3":"Sabbattha ca vippasadehi cittam; ","snp3.5:24.4":"Arammanam yajamanassa yanno, ","snp3.5:24.5":"Ettha patitthaya jahati dosam. ","snp3.5:25.1":"So vitarago pavineyya dosam, ","snp3.5:25.2":"Mettam cittam bhavayamappamanam; ","snp3.5:25.3":"Rattindivam satatamappamatto, ","snp3.5:25.4":"Sabba disa pharati appamannam”. ","snp3.5:26.1":"“Ko sujjhati muccati bajjhati ca, ","snp3.5:26.2":"Kenattana gacchati brahmalokam; ","snp3.5:26.3":"Ajanato me muni bruhi puttho, ","snp3.5:26.4":"Bhagava hi me sakkhi brahmajjadittho; ","snp3.5:26.5":"Tuvanhi no brahmasamosi saccam, ","snp3.5:26.6":"Katham upapajjati brahmalokam jutima”. ","snp3.5:27.1":"“Yo yajati tividham yannasampadam, ","snp3.5:27.2":"(maghati bhagava) ","snp3.5:27.3":"Aradhaye dakkhineyyebhi tadi; ","snp3.5:27.4":"Evam yajitva samma yacayogo, ","snp3.5:27.5":"Upapajjati brahmalokanti brumi”ti. ","snp3.5:28.1":"Evam vutte, magho manavo bhagavantam etadavoca: ","snp3.5:28.2":"“abhikkantam, bho gotama …pe… ","snp3.5:28.3":"ajjatagge panupetam saranam gatan”ti. ","snp3.5:28.4":"Maghasuttam pancamam. "}